# LEGACY (single-project layout). For the recommended per-project layout, put
# this file at config/projects/<name>/repos.list instead — see
# config/projects/example/. This top-level file is only used by the legacy
# docker-compose.yml stack.
#
# Repositories that make up your project. Copy to `config/repos.list`
# (gitignored) and list one SSH clone URL per line. All repos belong to the same
# project. Technology (Laravel / Next.js / Convex) is auto-detected after cloning.
#
# Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
#
# git@github.com:you/second-brain-backend.git
